    • Enum Constant Detail

      • AccessReason

        public static final AdwordsUserListField AccessReason
        Indicates the reason this account has been granted access to the list. The reason can be Shared, Owned, Licensed or Subscribed.

      • AccountUserListStatus

        public static final AdwordsUserListField AccountUserListStatus
        Indicates if this share is still active. When a UserList is shared with the user this field is set to Active. Later the userList owner can decide to revoke the share and make it Inactive. The default value of this field is set to Active.

      • ConversionTypes

        public static final AdwordsUserListField ConversionTypes
        Conversion types associated with this user list.

      • DateSpecificListEndDate

        public static final AdwordsUserListField DateSpecificListEndDate
        End date of users visit. If set to 20371230, then includes all users after startDate. The date's format should be YYYYMMDD. This field is selected by default.

      • DateSpecificListRule

        public static final AdwordsUserListField DateSpecificListRule
        Boolean rule that defines visitor of a page. This field is selected by default.

      • DateSpecificListStartDate

        public static final AdwordsUserListField DateSpecificListStartDate
        Start date of users visit. If set to 20000101, then includes all users before endDate. The date's format should be YYYYMMDD. This field is selected by default.

      • Description

        public static final AdwordsUserListField Description
        Description of this user list.

      • ExpressionListRule

        public static final AdwordsUserListField ExpressionListRule
        Boolean rule that defines this user list. The rule consists of a list of rule item groups. All the rule item groups are ORed for the evaluation. This field is selected by default.

      • Id

        public static final AdwordsUserListField Id
        Id of this user list.

      • IntegrationCode

        public static final AdwordsUserListField IntegrationCode
        An Id from external system. It is used by user list sellers to correlate ids on their systems.

      • IsReadOnly

        public static final AdwordsUserListField IsReadOnly
        A flag that indicates if a user may edit a list. Depends on the list ownership and list type. For example, external remarketing user lists are not editable.

      • ListType

        public static final AdwordsUserListField ListType
        Type of this list: remarketing/logical/external remarketing.

      • MembershipLifeSpan

        public static final AdwordsUserListField MembershipLifeSpan
        Number of days a user's cookie stays on your list since its most recent addition to the list.

      • Name

        public static final AdwordsUserListField Name
        Name of this user list. Depending on its AccessReason, the user list name may not be unique (e.g. if AccessReason=SHARED).

      • Rules

        public static final AdwordsUserListField Rules
        Logical list rules that define this user list. The rules are defined as logical operator (ALL/ANY/NONE) and a list of user lists. All the rules are anded for the evaluation.

      • SeedListSize

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SeedListSize
        Estimated number of users in this seed user list. This value is null if the number of users has not yet been determined.

      • SeedUserListDescription

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SeedUserListDescription
        Description of this seed user list.

      • SeedUserListId

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SeedUserListId
        Seed UserListId from which this list is derived.

      • SeedUserListName

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SeedUserListName
        Name of the seed user list.

      • SeedUserListStatus

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SeedUserListStatus
        Membership status of this seed user list.

      • Size

        public static final AdwordsUserListField Size
        Estimated number of users in this user list, on the Google Display Network. This value is null if the number of users has not yet been determined.

      • SizeForSearch

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SizeForSearch
        Estimated number of users in this user list in the google.com domain. These are the users available for targeting in search campaigns. This value is null if the number of users has not yet been determined.

      • SizeRange

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SizeRange
        Size range in terms of number of users of the UserList.

      • SizeRangeForSearch

        public static final AdwordsUserListField SizeRangeForSearch
        Size range in terms of number of users of the UserList, for Search ads.

      • Status

        public static final AdwordsUserListField Status
        Membership status of this user list. Indicates whether a user list is open or active. Only open user lists can accumulate more users and can be targeted to.
